name: Little Fairy Princess Party
description:
Fairy Princess Printable Digital Invite 

A digital invitation file in JPEG or PDF format will be personalized with your message and sent to your Etsy email address. No physical products will be shipped.

How to print digital invite:

1. You can print these at home on photo paper or heavy white cardsock
2. Take file (saved on a disk) to a local photo printer or office store
3. Upload to an online printing service like Vistaprint, FedEx Kinkos, etc.

Ordering

Please choose your Invite size (4x6 or 5x7) in the box below

***When checking out through Paypal please include the exact text you would like included on your invitation.

After your order is received I will send you (within 24 hrs.) a low resolution proof for you to approve. Once approved I will send you the high resolution file of your invite.

Graphics are designed by Zenware Designs from My Grafico.

*Files are for personal use only. You may not share, sell, or distribute the file any way.
